Enum Class ErrorMsgsEnum

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ErrorMsgsEnum>
cz.cvut.copakond.sweetfluffysheep.model.utils.enums.ErrorMsgsEnum
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ErrorMsgsEnum>, Constable
public enum ErrorMsgsEnum extends Enum<ErrorMsgsEnum>
Enum representing all error messages used in the game. This enum is used to define all error messages that can be displayed to the user. It is used in the game to provide feedback to the user when an error occurs.
